author: ian_dickinson
msg: Changes to listing and testing individuals, to account for edge cases (specifically: when a user has materialised entailments from an inference model into a plain model, which is a recommended design pattern). Also unified the implementations of OntResource.isIndividual() and OntModel.listIndividuals(), at the possible risk of some slowdown in listIndividuals on DB-backed models
